LEPROSY - USA (02): (AL) HUMAN, ARMADILLO, TRANSMISSION, IMPORTED, SUSPECTED, REQUEST FOR INFORMATION
*******************************************************************************************************
A ProMED-mail post
http://www.promedmail.org
